// Damage Shader: Set's the threshold for the darkest pixels (mark0) and the lightest pixels (mark1). If the threshold meets mark0, then "color1" is returned. If it fails and meets the threshold of mark1, then "color2" is returned. If there are any pixels lighter than that, then "color3" is returned. Note that this is used for ALL flashing effects.
// Defaults: 0.100 / 0.725
